{"data": {"repository": {"pullRequest": {"id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0NDI0MTE2MTA4", "number": 1769, "title": "Briefing room fixes", "bodyText": "This PR addresses several graphical issues in the Briefing Room tab. The main fix is for #1768 where the TO&E reports for a scenario were being cut off. However, I was also annoyed about how the various text areas were leaving a bunch of white space, so I made some changes to the grid bag layout to fix that.\nHere is a shot of what the it looks like before:\n\nHere is a shot of what it looks like after:\n\nI did have to unsnarl a bit of code to get it all working. Most importantly I passed the scenarioTable object into the MissionViewPanel where it is displayed so that there is only one scroll bar on the left. In order to do that without duplicating a bunch of code, I removed the separate ContractViewPanel and AtBContractViewPanel classes and consolidated them with MissionViewPanel. The only area where they differed was the fillStats function so this was relatively straightforward.", "createdAt": "2020-05-27T21:11:35Z", "url": "https://github.com/MegaMek/mekhq/pull/1769", "merged": true, "mergeCommit": {"oid": "7c44510e5401866bdf14dc0f276b2203c694cefb"}, "closed": true, "closedAt": "2020-06-01T18:16:37Z", "author": {"login": "AaronGullickson"}, "timelineItems": {"totalCount": 6, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABcldoo9gH2gAyNDI0MTE2MTA4OmEzMWU3MTM2YjYzMDU3N2EyYTAyNGM1NTgzMGUzZGY2YzI4ZTcwZjE=", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABclwsKxAFqTQyMDMwMjA0NQ==", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "a31e7136b630577a2a024c55830e3df6c28e70f1", "author": {"user": {"login": "AaronGullickson", "name": "Aaron Gullickson"}}, "url": "https://github.com/MegaMek/mekhq/commit/a31e7136b630577a2a024c55830e3df6c28e70f1", "committedDate": "2020-05-27T18:32:55Z", "message": "fixes Issue #1768: issue with TOE cutoff in scenario view"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequ